  "title": "Aesthetician",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Highlights:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Attractive Overall Salary Package (With Basic $2,800 + Incentive + Sales Comms)</li>\n  <li>Provide systematic training (Both Theory &amp; Hands-on)</li>\n  <li>6 Days: Mon-Fri 10am -8pm (break 1 hr); Sat 10am-7pm (break 1hr); Sun &amp; PH: Off</li>\n  <li>6 Off days/ month</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Job Description:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Perform facial, body, and device-based treatments (e.g. Hydrafacial, IPL, Fat Freezing) safely and effectively</li>\n  <li>Understand customers' skin/body goals and recommend suitable treatments, working with the doctor’s advice</li>\n  <li>Do basic skin and body analysis before treatments</li>\n  <li>Promote the company’s products and services</li>\n  <li>Keep treatment rooms clean, tidy, and presentable at all times</li>\n  <li>Provide friendly and professional customer service</li>\n  <li>Build good relationships with customers to encourage repeat visits</li>\n  <li>Meet and exceed personal sales and treatment targets</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>No prior experience required (training provided)</li>\n  <li>Relevant certifications (CIDESCO, CIBTEC, ITEC, etc.) will be an advantage</li>\n  <li>Strong customer service skills and a positive attitude</li>\n  <li>Well-groomed, motivated, and sales/service-oriented</li>\n  <li>Excellent interpersonal and communication skills</li>\n  <li>Able to work on weekends and retail hours</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></p>",
